    "Title": "Wanna be a Headhunter?",
    "Description": "You know us. You know what we do. System\u2019s getting a little crowded, so we\u2019re looking for some good soldiers to help keep our place here.\n\nIf you\u2019re up for it and don\u2019t mind getting your hands dirty, we\u2019ve got something to prove you\u2019ve got the stuff we\u2019re looking for.\n\n~mission(TargetName) was a former member who sold us out to XenoThreat and got some of their brothers and sisters killed. Now they think they can just live their life without consequence.\n\nYou take them out. You get boosted in. Sounds like a fair trade.\n\nThey\u2019ve been spotted around ~mission(Location|Address), so get there and take care of it.\n\nStows out.",
